                                                                                             NIST SP 800-128             GUIDE FOR SECURITY-FOCUSED CONFIGURATION MANAGEMENT OF INFORMATION SYSTEMS
                                                                                             _______________________________________________________________________________________________


                                                                                                  federal information system       An information system used or operated by an executive
                                                                                                  [40 USC 11331]                   agency, by a contractor of an executive agency, or by another
                                                                                                                                   organization on behalf of an executive agency.

                                                                                                  host-based intrusion             A program that monitors the characteristics of a single host and
                                                                                                  detection and prevention         the events occurring within that host to identify and stop
                                                                                                  system                           suspicious activity.
                                                                                                  [SP 800-94]

                                                                                                  incident                         An occurrence that actually or potentially jeopardizes, without
                                                                                                  [44 USC 3552]                    lawful authority, the confidentiality, integrity, or availability of
                                                                                                                                   information or an information system; or constitutes a violation
                                                                                                                                   or imminent threat of violation of security policies, security
This publication is available free of charge from: https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.SP.800-128




                                                                                                                                   procedures, or acceptable use policies.

                                                                                                  information resources            Information and related resources, such as personnel,
                                                                                                  [44 USC 3502]                    equipment, funds, and information technology.

                                                                                                  information security             The protection of information and systems from unauthorized
                                                                                                  [44 USC 3552]                    access, use, disclosure, disruption, modification, or destruction
                                                                                                                                   in order to provide confidentiality, integrity, and availability.

                                                                                                  information system               A discrete set of information resources organized for the
                                                                                                  [44 USC 3502]                    collection, processing, maintenance, use, sharing,
                                                                                                                                   dissemination, or disposition of information.

                                                                                                  information system               A discrete identifiable IT asset that represents a building block
                                                                                                  component                        of an information system.

                                                                                                  information system               A descriptive record of components within an information
                                                                                                  component inventory              system.

                                                                                                  information system               A formal document that provides an overview of the security
                                                                                                  security plan                    requirements for an information system and describes the
                                                                                                  [OMB A-130]                      security controls in place or planned for meeting those
                                                                                                                                   requirements.




